# Development Roadmap

Read `docs/ROADMAP.md` before starting new features or modules.

## Stack
- Patient: React Native (Expo) — `apps/patient-mobile`
- Doctor/admin: Next.js — `apps/doctor-admin`
- Backend: Supabase + Node.js — `apps/backend`, `supabase/`
- Shared types: `packages/shared-types`

## Build order (do not skip ahead)
0. Foundation → 1. Auth → 2. Profiles → 3. Booking → 4. Payments
→ 5. Chat → 6. Rx + SOAP → 7. Closure + ratings → 8. Analytics/admin
→ **9. Audio/video (LAST — not priority)**

## Deferred (Phase 9 only)
Voice/video calls, call logging, missed-call notifications, callback requests.

## When implementing a feature
1. Check which phase it belongs to in `docs/ROADMAP.md`
2. Do not build Phase 9 features until Phases 0–8 are stable
3. Extend `packages/shared-types` when adding new entities
